```

const editDialog = this.dialogRef.open(EditComponent, { 
...
}); 

editDialog.afterClosed().subscribe( result =&gt; {
    if (result) {
       let confirmDialog = this.dialogRef.open(ConfirmDialog, {...});
       confirmDialog.afterClosed().subscribe( result =&gt; {
            ...
       });

    }
});
```

If you are trying to kick off that from the dialog, then you can create a new confirmation dialog from the edit dialog and based on the result from that, return your response back to the grid component.

